summary: Just a save game in Helgen keep. Maxed out all perks, max skills
descriptionHtml:
Carla is at Helgen keep after having chosen the imperial side and following Hadvar. 

Player is maxed out on perks and skills, if you want to start fresh you can remove everything with the console. I\'ll try to upload a clean save of her later! 

Please endorse it if you like it! 

Has a few mods installed but don\'t worry should look/work fine without.

Recommended but NOT required:
No more blocky faces   http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
Detailed bodies  http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=256
High Quality Eyes   http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
Jaysus Swords   http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1002
author: Blindwinter
